  Demi wore a dark red bikini top, which helped highlight her enviable curves. She paired it with a matching thong, leaving her fans little to the imagination. Demi also tied a delicate green and gold, embroidered wrap around her waist as she lounged on the deck of a boat. She wore her long hair down with a few small braids running through it, tagging hairstylist Federico D’Abate.  The social media star opted for a glossy makeup look, perfected by makeup artist Aaliyah Diaz. Demi posed with a beautiful ocean backdrop behind her, complete with a rocky cove. The glamorous influencer captioned the picture: “Me, myself and I.” Demi is no stranger to a daring bikini pic, regularly posting them to Instagram as she travels the globe.   